org.xlattice.corexml.expr

Class NodeSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.corexml.expr.Expr
      • org.xlattice.corexml.expr.NodeSet

  • public class NodeSet
extends Expr
    A container for unique Nodes. No ordering is guaranteed on the set.

    NodeSets are one of the fundamental XPath data types. Typically they represent the set of XML nodes which match a query.

    This implementation is not synchronized.

    Author:
    Jim Dixon
